Son of Uriah Cardozo and his wife Marie Nicholson, of Aeux, Cayes, Haiti, West Indies. Born at Kingston, Jamaica. Educated at the Petit Seminaire College, St. Martial, Port-au-Prince, Haiti; and at St. George's College, Kingston, Jamaica.
